args "--unamed-opts --no-handle-error --long-help -a glod_args_info -f glod_parser"
package "terms"
usage "terms [OPTIONS...] [FILE]..."
description "Output terms of FILEs.

A term (by our definition) is a sequence of alphanumerical characters \
that can be interluded (but not prefixed or suffixed) by punctuation \
characters.

In this sense company names like AT&T or email addresses a@b.com will \
count as one term."

